"{\"uid\": \"washingtontimes.com-news-2024-aug-12-tom-daley-five-time-olympic-medalist-announces-ret\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LONDON (AP) - Five-time Olympic medalist Tom Daley has announced his retirement from diving.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9998261236245899, \"rank\": 0.00015254111025555714, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.620233189974984e-37, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old, who won gold at Tokyo in 2021, said he had decided to call time on his career during an interview with British Vogue.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9258767712213275, \"rank\": 0.08004196406128009, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 214, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.320139338934198e-19, \"text\": \"British Vogue\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's Daley, who claimed his fifth Olympic medal with silver in the 10m synchronized event in Paris last month, said: \\\"It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9637707540510292, \"rank\": 0.03643737625780613, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999998634399981, \"rank\": 1.3656018275782847e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectations.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when I walked out and saw my husband (Lance) and kids (Robbie and Phoenix) and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9766511896354385, \"rank\": 0.011526895929303546, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"score\": 0.6456582178996904, \"rank\": 0.5140502659281324, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Suns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the right time to call it a day.\\\"\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 The Washington Times, LLC.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9996499199522751, \"rank\": 0.0003500186824606355, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEE MORE VIDEOS  Where's Islamic extremism in National Guard shooting discussion?\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 0.9972706494386975, \"rank\": 0.0025434545612659635, \"text\": \"Islamic extremism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}, {\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Guard_of_Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9238620393175827, \"rank\": 0.045425940463442366, \"text\": \"National Guard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Guard_of_Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Guard_of_Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morality key in keeping AI safe  Zelenskyy (still) does not have the cards to beat Russia\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9997748589317836, \"rank\": 0.00022369149581751255, \"text\": 